5 person specified by the court;
6 3. Approaching the petitioner or other person specified by the court within
7 a distance specified in the order, not to exceed five hundred (500) feet;
8 4. Going to or within a specified distance of a specifically described
9 residence, school, or place of employment or area where such a place is
10 located; and
11 5. Disposing of or damaging any of the property of the parties;
